To specify a buffer size of 10 megabytes, 10 and 10MB are equivalent. A size threshold of 256 bytes can be specified as 256 or 256B.

You can also use any of the supported units. These are:

- B for bytes
- KB for kilobytes
- MB for megabytes
- GB for gigabytes
- TB for terabytes

